Open the Item Journals page:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000480-0/10HandlingUnitsManagement.png"><br><br>

Indicate a positive adjustment for the item (eg. 1120). Enter the location code and quantity. You can enter the handling unit No. by choosing it from the list or by creating a new one.


If we indicate only the No. of packaging material **automatically the system will create the handling unit during posting. **

